Unprotect for DUNE 1992 by Virgin Games VGA version
First, copy all original disks and install to your hard disk from the copies
only! Next, copy this file, DUNEPRG.EXE, to where you installed the game,
overwriting the old file of the same name.
Run the game normally. The doc check asking you what page in the manual a
certain picture appears WILL NOT come up. It has been bypassed.
Also, you might want to copy this file to the backup copy of disk #1, so it too
is backed up. DO NOT ALTER YOUR ORIGINAL DISKS! COPY THEM USING DOS DISKCOPY AND
COPY THIS EXE FILE TO YOUR COPY OF DISK ONE! Enjoy.